snippet.title: Best VGM 610 - Mega Man 2 - Flash Man Stage
snippet.description:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Megaman 2 (1989)
Flashman Stage
Manami Matsumae, Yoshihiro Sakaguchi & Ogeretsu Kun
